latestPosts.caption:
It was a wonderful experience being one of the judges for North East Dancing Superstar Season 4. All of us were in awe of the talents that we saw and it was quite the event with so many countless kids and young adults performing their hearts out. Although we had to settle for a select few to be moved towards the finals and be declared winners ultimately, I believe that almost everyone who showed their talents were worthy of so much. My congratulations and best wishes to all the winners and my dearest participants.

My heart, prayers and best wishes are with all of you.
